---
title: Tex-Mex Tofu Hash with Chipotle Mayo
description: Fancy some breakfast vibes for dinner tonight? Potatoes, hot peppers, corn and tomatoes are roasted to achieve beautiful caramelization before being tossed with tofu, onions and spices to create a heavenly hash.
